{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.finish()","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>finish()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">El método <strong><code>finish()</code> </strong>de la interfaz&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a>&nbsp; </span>establece el tiempo de reproducción actual hasta el final de la animación correspondiente a la dirección de reproducción actual. Es decir, si la animación se está reproduciendo hacia adelante, establece el tiempo de reproducción a la longitud de la secuencia de animación, y si la animación se reproduce hacia atras , (habiendo llamado a su método <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\" title=\"reverse()\"><code>reverse()</code></a>), establece el tiempo de la reproducción en 0.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>Animation</em>.finish(); </pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parámetros","title":"Parámetros","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_devuelto","title":"Valor devuelto","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>\n\n<dl>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"excepciones","title":"Excepciones","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"invalidstate\"><code>InvalidState</code></dt>\n <dd>La velocidad de reproducción del reproductor es 0 o la velocidad de reproducción de la animación es mayor que 0 y el tiempo de finalización de la animación es infinito.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"<strong>Ejemplos</strong>","isH3":false,"content":"<p>El siguiente ejemplo muestra cómo usar el método <code>finish()</code> y captura un error <code>InvalidState</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>interfaceElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mousedown\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    player<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">finish</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> e <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">InvalidState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"finish() called on paused or finished animation.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">logMyErrors</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//pasa el objeto excepción al manejador de errores.</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>El siguiente ejemplo finaliza todas las animaciones en un solo elemento, independientemente de su dirección de reproducción.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAnimations</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">finish</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Ejemplos"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-finish\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'finish()' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.finish","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> para otros métodos y propiedades que puede usar para controlar la animación de la página web.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>Animation.play()</code></a> para reproducir una animación hacia adelante.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>Animation.reverse()</code></a> para reproducir una animación hacia atrás.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"<strong>Ejemplos</strong>","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"El método finish() de la interfaz Animation de la Web Animations API  ","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.finish()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation.finish()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/finish","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/finish/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish","title":"Animation.finish()"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.finish() - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}